actions.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.
Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

official_title: Providing amounts from the contingent fund of the House for continuing expenses of investigations and studies by the standing and select committees of the House from April 1, 1992, through April 30, 1992.

summary.text: Makes available from the contingent fund of the House of Representatives amounts necessary for continued investigations and studies by each standing and select committee of the House in the second session of the 102d Congress between March 31, 1992, and April 30, 1992.
